ed="T" n="0807b18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0807b18"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>京兆聖壽寺<persName key="A011526">慧靈</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0807b19"/><persName key="A011526">釋慧靈</persName>，未詳何許人也。幼脫塵機，勤從誦<lb
ed="T" n="0807b20"/>習，及當應法，戒品方圓，銳意毘尼，探<anchor xml:id="beg0807004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>頤</sic><corr>賾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0807004"/>持<lb
ed="T" n="0807b21"/>犯，以行副解，心口相符。由是講訓，名望翕<lb
ed="T" n="0807b22"/>如也。人皆奉畏，神明如也。<date from-iso="+0853-02-16" key="j20326592033012" to-iso="+0854-02-04"><name>大中</name>七年</date>，<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>幸<lb
ed="T" n="0807b23"/><placeName key="PL000000042412">莊嚴寺</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0807sgsz7"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0807sgsz7"/>佛牙，登大塔，<persName key="A003667">宣</persName>問耆年，乃賜紫<lb
ed="T" n="0807b24"/>衣。<date from-iso="+0853-07-14" key="j20328072032836" to-iso="+0853-08-12">其年六月</date>，勅補<persName key="A011526">靈</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000042412">新寺</placeName>上座矣。<persName key="A003667">帝</persName>望<lb
ed="T" n="0807b25"/>寺西北廢<placeName key="PL000000042422">總持寺</placeName>，乃下勅曰：「<persName key="A003667">朕</persName>以政閑賞<lb
ed="T" n="0807b26"/>景，幸于<placeName key="PL000000042412">莊嚴</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000042412">其寺</placeName>複殿重廊，連甍比棟。幽房<lb
ed="T" n="0807b27"/>祕宇，窈窕疏通，密竹翠松，垂陰擢秀，行而迷<lb
ed="T" n="0807b28"/>道，天下<name>梵</name>宮，高明寡匹。當建之時，以京城<lb
ed="T" n="0807b29"/>西<placeName key="PL000000042412">昆明池</placeName>勢微下，乃建木浮圖，高三百尺。藩<pb ed="T" n="0807c" xml:id="T50.2061.0807c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0807c01"/>邸之時，遊此<placeName key="PL000000042412">伽藍</placeName>，覩斯勝事。其<placeName key="PL000000042422">總持寺</placeName>，<date from-iso="+0605-01-28" key="j19420591946768" to-iso="+0617-12-20"><name>大業</name></date><lb
ed="T" n="0807c02"/>中立，規制與<placeName key="PL000000042412">莊嚴寺</placeName>正同，今容像則毀，忍<lb
ed="T" n="0807c03"/>草隨荒，香徑蕪侵，尚存基址。<placeName key="PL000000042422">其寺</placeName>宜許重<lb
ed="T" n="0807c04"/>建，以副予心。」三月十一日<!--找不到此時間-->，令三教首座<persName key="A011954">辯章</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0807c05"/>勾當修<placeName key="PL000000042422">寺</placeName>，及畢工，推<persName key="A011526">靈</persName>為綱任，崇聖寺<!--找不到此地-->賜<lb
ed="T" n="0807c06"/>紫<persName key="A019408">叡川</persName>充寺主，<placeName key="PL000000042216">福壽寺</placeName>臨壇大德賜紫<persName key="A009180">玄暢</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0807c07"/>充都維那。<persName key="A011526">靈</persName>居寺職，清眾咸序，<ref type="person" target="#A003667">帝</ref>所欽重。<lb
ed="T" n="0807c08"/>寺中常貢梨<anchor xml:id="beg0807sgsz9"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0807sgsz9"/>蜜，其色白，其味愈常，蠟房所<lb
ed="T" n="0807c09"/>取者。<persName key="A011526">靈</persName>居<placeName key="PL000000042412">新寺</placeName>終矣。究其<persName key="A011526">靈公</persName>如曾預<date notBefore-iso="+0765-01-30" key="j20005002001190" notAfter-iso="+0766-12-21">代<lb
ed="T" n="0807c10"/>宗<name>永泰</name>中</date>參譯證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>，則可年百奇歲矣。如不<lb
ed="T" n="0807c11"/>見<persName key="A000095">不空</persName>、<persName key="A000540">良賁</persName>，乃春秋夏臘無理知焉。</p>
